reviewText:
I really enjoyed this movie. Kim Ha Neul is one of my favorite actresses. She was so funny in the series Gentlemens Dignity. I look forward to watching more of these kind of films!!
Thank you, Rose Ralph

This was also heartwarming.  The girl in the story was trying to escape her old life & a mistake for a place where she could be someone else, someplace better.  She found a place peopled by folks who did not judge.  Would she stay and would she trust again?  Gently acted & slowly paced, I know this sweet tale is for me, a keeper.
